{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/clea_banner.jpg?t=1737936880\" /><br><br>Mum and Dad have been experimenting on Chaos Servants, but now, the monsters have been let loose. Clea, with her brother in tow, must escape from the Whitlock Mansion.<br><br>Watch your back, Clea. Those closest to you may be the real terror.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/clea_1_sneak_gif.gif?t=1737936880\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Skill-focused horror:</h2><br>Clea is primarily a test of skills. Enemies roam the halls dynamically in real-time, reacting to the players' every noise. Clea is a challenging title, rewarding those who have mastered its mechanics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Outwit the Chaos Servants:</h2><br>The Chaos Servants are on the hunt. Listen for their footsteps, peek under doors, and stay far, far away.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/clea_1_toilet_gif.gif?t=1737936880\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Escape the Whitlock Mansion:</h2><br>The Whitlock family has trapped Clea inside the mansion. Hunt down key items and solve the puzzles designed to lock you from the outside world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">No jump scares:</h2><br>No prescripted scares, promise. Your skills and actions will determine Clea's fate.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/981020/extras/clea_1_wit_gif.gif?t=1737936880\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unveil family history:</h2><br>The Whitlock bloodline is filled with dark memories. Obtain memory orbs and uncover your family secrets through bonus chapters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Voice cast:</h2><br>Clea \u2013 Xanthe Huynh, Edmond \u2013 Anairis Quinones, Florine, Mum \u2013 Aimee Smith, Dad \u2013 Miguel Moran, Maids \u2013 Angela Tran","achievements":{"highl